Program: Outlook
Title: "I went to my own funeral"
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0104hn0
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 6 Nov 2012
The Brazilian man who came home to find his family holding his funeral describes their joy at discovering he was not the man lying in the coffin. Matthew Bannister also talks to the American fighter pilot who's become friends with the Serbian gunner who shot down his plane. The Afghan woman who's following in her father's footsteps by playing international football. Image: Outlook presenter Matthew Bannister Show less